window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Mason, Blake and their allies in Nassau are still alive in the Great Game. But for how much longer?</p> <p>While trying to protect and recruit more players and civilians from another settlement, Mason has fallen into a mortal dungeonâ€”The Great Devourer's Lair.</p> <p>It wasn't meant to be found so soon. It was designed for a later stage in the game when players would have more power. But what secrets might the dungeon hold? If Mason and his new player friend Carl can survive it, just how powerful could it make them?</p> <p>There's only one way to find out....</p> <p>With millions of views on Royal Road and Scribblehub, this series has more than 10 books worth of story, and more to come!</p>"; 
